    <item>
      <title>阿根廷说，其新的国际货币基金组织计划将总计200亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/argentina-s-new-imf-program-will-be-for-20-billion-caputo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济部长路易斯·卡普托（Luis Caputo）表示，阿根廷在国际货币基金组织中的未来计划将以200亿美元的价格为20亿美元，而执行董事会的批准可能需要数周的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/argentina-s-new-imf-program-will-be-for-20-billion-caputo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 12:41:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼克斯广播公司获得一周的缓刑，以解决无偿债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/knicks-broadcaster-gets-a-week-s-reprieve-to-resolve-unpaid-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MSG Networks刚刚获得了为期一周的延期，以与贷方以超过8亿美元的债务进行谈判，以挽救詹姆斯·多兰（James Dolan）主持的公司免于Collapse。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/knicks-broadcaster-gets-a-week-s-reprieve-to-resolve-unpaid-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 12:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲汽油价格边缘提高，因为储存补充织机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-gas-prices-steady-as-heating-demand-winds-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格在整天波动后升高，因为暖气季节达到了最后，交易者专注于明年冬天的储存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-gas-prices-steady-as-heating-demand-winds-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 08:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的担忧，股票流失抵消固体数据：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国对汽车制造商的关税提前，股票波动，尽管数据显示出显示全球最大经济体的增长速度快，但对贸易战争的经济影响表示了担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 22:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
